00:00:17,397 --> 00:00:19,274
<i>Mystery on Bardotta!</i>

20
00:00:19,357 --> 00:00:21,693
<i>An oasis of peace
during the Clone Wars.</i>

21
00:00:21,776 --> 00:00:24,779
<i>The galaxy-wide conflict now threatens
the ancient ways</i>

22
00:00:24,863 --> 00:00:26,281
<i>of the Bar dot tan people.</i>

23
00:00:26,364 --> 00:00:29,451
<i>With their spiritual leaders
mysteriously vanishing,</i>

24
00:00:29,534 --> 00:00:32,787
<i>the foundations of order in its system
are near collapse.</i>

25
00:00:32,871 --> 00:00:36,958
<i>In desperation, the Queen of Bardotta
has called upon the Republic Senate</i>

26
00:00:37,042 --> 00:00:42,214
<i>with a puzzling request, to help save
her people from certain doom.</i>

27
00:00:42,297 --> 00:00:45,133
<i>I have humbly come before you
to ask for assistance</i>

28
00:00:45,217 --> 00:00:47,594
<i>in our time of need, Chancellor.</i>

29
00:00:47,802 --> 00:00:52,807
Queen Julia, the Republic is honored
that you have come to us for aid.

30
00:00:53,725 --> 00:00:59,481
We are always happy to support
the neutral systems in a time of crisis.

31
00:00:59,606 --> 00:01:02,984
If I may introduce
two of our best ambassadors...

32
00:01:03,109 --> 00:01:05,570
<i>With all due respect, Chancellor,</i>

33
00:01:05,654 --> 00:01:09,407
<i>there is only one person
in the Republic I will meet with.</i>

34
00:01:15,163 --> 00:01:17,123
Representative Binks?

35
00:01:17,290 --> 00:01:20,961
Why would the Queen of Bardotta
request the presence of Jar Jar Binks?

36
00:01:21,044 --> 00:01:22,629
<i>I'm afraid she would not say,</i>

37
00:01:22,712 --> 00:01:26,591
<i>but she impressed upon the Senate
the urgency of their situation.</i>

38
00:01:26,675 --> 00:01:29,844
And what exactly is the trouble
on Bardotta?

39
00:01:29,928 --> 00:01:32,597
<i>Several of the ancient mystics,</i>

40
00:01:32,681 --> 00:01:35,809
<i>the Dagoyan Masters,
have disappeared.</i>

41
00:01:35,892 --> 00:01:39,646
A strong connection to the Force
the Dagoyan Masters have.

42
00:01:39,729 --> 00:01:45,026
Yet, unlike the Jedi or Sith they are.
Warriors, they are not.

43
00:01:45,735 --> 00:01:50,532
Intuition, knowledge, the harmony
of the universe is what they sense.

44
00:01:51,366 --> 00:01:53,910
Passively they connect with the Force.

45
00:01:54,035 --> 00:01:59,291
<i>I wonder why the Queen doesn't want
a Jedi sent to solve this mystery?</i>

46
00:01:59,374 --> 00:02:03,837
Long ago inducted into the Jedi Order
Bar dot tan children were.

47
00:02:03,962 --> 00:02:07,841
However, thieves the Jedi
were named by the Dagoyan.

48
00:02:07,924 --> 00:02:11,469
The Dagoyan Masters believed the Jedi
took the children against their will,

49
00:02:11,553 --> 00:02:13,888
