50
00:02:13,972 --> 00:02:16,266
Chancellor, am I to understand
the Queen requested

51
00:02:16,349 --> 00:02:19,144
Representative Binks
go alone to Bardotta?

52
00:02:19,227 --> 00:02:22,439
<i>I'm afraid she was quite specific
on that point.</i>

53
00:02:22,522 --> 00:02:25,483
