67
00:03:49,776 --> 00:03:53,363
Mesa Representative Binks
of the Republic Senate

68
00:03:53,446 --> 00:03:55,323
and hesa with mesa.

69
00:03:55,698 --> 00:04:00,954
Representative Binks, you are an
honored guest of the Queen. Come!

70
