why have you brought this Jedi
to Bardotta?

72
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:42,120
Oh, Great Queenie Julia,
please forgive mesa.

73
00:04:42,287 --> 00:04:43,955
Disa Jedi is mesa patio,

74
